{"_path":"/maps/_devops/version-control","_dir":"_devops","_draft":false,"_partial":true,"_locale":"","title":"版本管理","description":"版本管理是一种软件开发过程中的管理方法，它通过对软件的版本号进行管理，以便于开发者和用户了解软件的变动情况。","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"源码管理"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"源码管理"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"/maps/_devops/git"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Git"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"/maps/_devops/git/gitflow"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Gitflow"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"TODO："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://sapling-scm.com/docs/introduction/differences-git","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Sapling"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"版本号管理"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"版本号管理"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"语义化版本是什么"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"语义化版本是什么？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"语义化版本（Semantic Version）是一种版本号码标记方法，它要求版本号由“主版本号。次版本号。修订号”组成，分别代表不兼容的 API 改动、向下兼容的功能性改动或新增、向下兼容的问题修正。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://semver.org/lang/zh-CN/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"语义化版本 @semver.org"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"语义化版本解决了什么问题"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"语义化版本解决了什么问题？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Semver 被设计用来解决依赖地狱的问题，常用于定义了公共 API 的项目，因为其各个版本号的意义都和 API 的变动挂钩。但 Semver 从某种意义上来说过于理想化，主要因为实际开发中代码变动没用绝对意义上的 no breaking change 这么一说。bug 和 breaking change 的界限本身就很模糊，所以实际上，任何改动都可能带来意料之外的 breaking change。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"许多项目并不遵循 Semver，如 TS 的开发者声称，其 minor 版本可能引入 Breaking Change，见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://github.com/microsoft/TypeScript/issues/14116","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"TypeScript should follow semantic versioning @GitHub"}]},{"type":"text","value":"。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"如何解决版本号膨胀问题"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"如何解决版本号膨胀问题？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"在单仓多包项目中，如果遵循语义化版本，那么版本同步会使版本号迅速膨胀。一个好的方案是现在其他项目使用 0.x 版本号开发，等 API 稳定后再合并到单仓中升级成为 1.0.0 版本。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://medium.com/netscape/the-case-for-monorepos-907c1361708a","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"The Case for MonoreposJJJ"}]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"源码管理","depth":2,"text":"源码管理"},{"id":"版本号管理","depth":2,"text":"版本号管理"}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:6.maps:_devops:version-control.md","_source":"content","_file":"6.maps/_devops/version-control.md","_stem":"6.maps/_devops/version-control","_extension":"md"}